hooks.prompt:
Output ONLY raw JSON, no markdown, no code blocks, no extra text.

Scan $ARGUMENTS for tool calls matching 'codegen_create_run' or 'codegen_get_run'. Extract run ID, status, web_url, and any PR links.

If no runs found: {"ok":true,"reason":"No Codegen runs this session."}
If runs found: {"ok":true,"reason":"Codegen runs: #ID STATUS URL | Total: N"}
